plyTime":"2018-12-29T22:10:31.000Z","msg":"台灣人講野成日都無棱兩可咁<br />\n沒差、沒關係、還好、都可、還不錯....<br />\n有時都唔知係要定唔要 想定唔想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"泛民講野都無棱兩可啦<br />\n講民主講抗共<br />\n但反對港獨，要幫新支民<br />\n知道自己沒得兜攞唔到年輕票<br />\n就講「自決」<br />\n有時都唔知係反共定唔反共"},{"pid":"b60b65e0639a1f42bb0e28f51732d9f3023fb5f7","tid":961123,"uid":48728,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8c36bfc98e012d33e86f069032e6fb68fd039a3a","tid":961123,"uid":135278,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"368da01778f73e7a222b415398a15c6871c93bf6","tid":961123,"uid":29270,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"quote":{"pid":"4ab6506016ad0828b7cca11400bd00b9bf974dd4","tid":961123,"uid":45368,"like":51,"dislike":139,"score":-88,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T22:10:31.000Z","msg":"台灣人講野成日都無棱兩可咁<br />\n沒差、沒關係、還好、都可、還不錯....<br />\n有時都唔知係要定唔要 想定唔想"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T23:29:46.000Z","msg":"Q: 頭五日可否洗頭？<br />\nA: 沒差(冇分別)<br />\n<br />\n清楚到不得了，有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"問「可否」答「沒差」都清楚？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以就可以 唔可以就唔可以<br />\n「沒差」真係衰左啲 幾時見過龍應台出書會寫「沒差」<br />\n<br />\n唔係幫港女 純粹用中文角度去睇個對話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇用過是但同冇所謂答人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165213d95b1283981e56bdd247a6e596259f85b7","tid":961123,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67629a7a85c149900961ba21f50585c0f9265dfa","tid":961123,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"為何成功的人也說不沖涼不洗頭<br />\n<br />\n點解唔自己做下research ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.scrcivf.com/embryo-transfer-tips-for-before-and-after-the-procedure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.scrcivf.com%2Fembryo-transfer-tips-for-before-and-after-the-procedure&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=db550d13\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.scrcivf.com/embryo-transfer-tips-for-before-and-after-the-procedure</a><br />\n<br />\nWhat is embryo implantation?<br />\nImplantation occurs when an embryo attaches to the wall of the uterus in the endometrial lining. In IVF, it occurs six to ten days after the egg retrieval process, which is one to five days after the embryo transfer. This equates to days 20 to 24 of an ideal 28 day menstrual cycle.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Avoid extremes of temperature<br />\nHot tubs, saunas, hot yoga, or any activity that raises your internal temperature is something to avoid at this point. In general it&rsquo;s best not to be submerged in water such as pools or baths during this time, as it leaves you vulnerable to infection. Stick to a soothing hot shower until your doctor tells you otherwise.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.essentialbaby.com.au/forums/index.php?/topic/895425-having-a-bath-and-swimming-after-embryo-transfer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.essentialbaby.com.au%2Fforums%2Findex.php%3F%2Ftopic%2F895425-having-a-bath-and-swimming-after-embryo-transfer%2F&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7475a62c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.essentialbaby.com.au/forums/index.php?/topic/895425-having-a-bath-and-swimming-after-embryo-transfer/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hi PriLou,<br />\n<br />\nMy clinic advises no tub baths or swimming for 48 hours post embryo transfer. <br />\n<br />\nI'm guessing that after that is fine as long as you don't increase your core temp, so no hot baths or training for the olympic swim team<br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"仲要問？<br />\n因為個港女根本唔係&ldquo;港&rdquo;女<br />\n支那婆識撚英文咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b905caa74a8583ee1e066326ade2da784b1cb7c8","tid":961123,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"搞到香港又扣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d65503bb66bcf7e295a43e90df93e278764caab","tid":961123,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"白痴港女，洗頭關你d卵乜事"},{"pid":"7a74fa62a3945e5eae58d4e2a64a3c9bc4bcb3f9","tid":961123,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"為何成功的人也說不沖涼不洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982d41d1df4cc9bdff2e2d03b85a6329d2e2fe22","tid":961123,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"368da01778f73e7a222b415398a15c6871c93bf6","tid":961123,"uid":29270,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"quote":{"pid":"4ab6506016ad0828b7cca11400bd00b9bf974dd4","tid":961123,"uid":45368,"like":51,"dislike":139,"score":-88,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T22:10:31.000Z","msg":"台灣人講野成日都無棱兩可咁<br />\n沒差、沒關係、還好、都可、還不錯....<br />\n有時都唔知係要定唔要 想定唔想"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T23:29:46.000Z","msg":"Q: 頭五日可否洗頭？<br />\nA: 沒差(冇分別)<br />\n<br />\n清楚到不得了，有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"沒差 以為 &ldquo;你答的和我沒有差別&rdquo;<br />\n即係 &ldquo;你啱⋯&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n原來唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自膠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：80後"},{"pid":"531ad4acb6cdec67f0bcf5184676b19c98d8eece","tid":961123,"uid":30478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"唔明國語就咪問台灣醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f1ca25d88060a1211168a737099c1227411c00","tid